									Tous
								</button>
								<button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark tous-cours-filter-btn" data-filter="5g">
									5G
								</button>
								<button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark tous-cours-filter-btn" data-filter="coeur-reseau">
									 C≈ìur de r√©seau
